casebody.data:
Thursday, July 30, 1998

MOTION DOCKET

97-357. Westhaven, Inc. v. Wood Cty. Bd. of Revision.

Board of Tax Appeals, No. 95-P-1052. This cause came on for further consideration upon appellants’ motion to withdraw motion for reconsideration. Upon consideration thereof,

IT IS ORDERED by the court that the motion to withdraw motion for reconsideration be, and hereby is, granted.
